Class NullType

java.lang.Object
io.shiromi.saml.types.AbstractType<Object>
io.shiromi.saml.types.NullType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class NullType extends AbstractType<Object>
Instances of the class NullType all have a value of null, but can all be cast to the different types, it does not carry any special methods or has any special functionality

1.0
